message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: Auditions - Day 03 Extended]

𝗔𝗧𝗧𝗘𝗡𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡, 𝗧𝗥𝗢𝗢𝗣𝗦! 🚨

Due to today’s class suspension, command has issued an extension. 

Auditions will now continue until Friday, September 19, 2025. This gives all ITHM Tams soldiers more time to march in and prove their strength! 🪖

🗓️ 𝗡𝗲𝘄 𝗦𝗰𝗵𝗲𝗱𝘂𝗹𝗲: September 19, 2025 (6:00 PM – 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲: ARH Function Room 302-303
🔗 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 Walk-ins and duo’s are still welcome—so tighten your ranks, stay battle-ready, and let your skills take the front line. 🔰

The mission isn’t over yet—report for duty, soldiers! 💥

Pubmat By: Hisami Muramatsu
Caption By: Mae Saeed

message.text:
Forge onward, JPIAns!

The Associates Search 2025 welcomes you to lead and connect with your fellow JPIAns. Take this opportunity to enhance your Tamaraw journey. Become one of the knights, the associates of the Far Eastern University Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants, for this school year!

Step into your role as:

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

Let your skills be known and become part of FEU-JPIA Manila’s family by registering through the link below:
https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!

#AssociateSearch2025
#TamHunt2025
#FEUJPIA2526

message.text:
Forge onward, JPIAns!

The Associates Search 2025 welcomes you to lead and connect with your fellow JPIAns. Take this opportunity to enhance your Tamaraw journey. Become one of the knights, the associates of the Far Eastern University Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants, for this school year!

Step into your role as:

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

Let your skills be known and become part of FEU-JPIA Manila’s family by registering through the link below:
https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!

#AssociateSearch2025
#TamHunt2025
#FEUJPIA2526

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!
